---
title: Un-bear-lievable Uchucuta Inspired Cauliflower Salad with Smashed Potatoes, Peanuts and Soured Cream
description: Discover the traditional Peruvian salsa uchucuta, made with local herbs for a slightly sour and spicy sauce. This version with mint and lemon makes an easier sauce without the heat, instead spicing up the roasted cauliflower for a truly splendid salad.
